Class SiapParamSet

    public class SiapParamSet
extends ParamSet
implements java.lang.Iterable<Param>
    Construct an initial default parameter set containing the parameters for a SIAP service. Currently this paramset contains the combined parameters for all SIAP operations. A list of the currently defined parameters, including their name, type, and description, can be found in this table.
